# Synkra AIOS Development Rules

These rules configure the behavior of AI agents in this repository.

## 1. CLI First
- MUST: All features must work via CLI first.
- MUST: Dashboards only observe, they don't control.

## 2. Agent Authority
- @devops handles all Git pushes and PR creations.
- @architect makes all architecture decisions.
- @qa gives the final word on code quality.

## 3. Story-Driven Development
- docs/stories/ is the directory for all active development.
- Always use checkboxes [ ] and update the File List.

## 4. Quality Gates
- No merge without: `npm run lint`, `npm run typecheck`, `npm test`.
- Absolute imports with `@/` alias preferred.

## 5. Agent Shortcuts
- @dev, @qa, @architect, @pm, @po, @sm, @analyst, @devops
- Use `*help` for commands and `*exit` to stop.

---
*Follow .aios-core/constitution.md for full details.*
